name: Catalogue de l'École biblique et archéologique française de Jérusalem
description: The 'Catalogue de l'Ecole Biblique et Archaeologique Francaise/Catalogue of the French Biblical and Archaeological School of Jerusalem' is the electronic edition of the card catalogue database for the Ecole Biblique's library. **This resource is only accessible in Bobst Library. To use this resource, stop by the 5th floor Reference Center.
